The paper discusses image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of wavelets and optimization techniques also suggests a connection to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The development of a software tool for image processing could also fall under data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
